This is related to a previously closed bug:

https://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRA-36583

Currently, the product is not designed to retain redirect information and history in an XML backup for tickets that were previously moved between projects. The issue this causes is that if a user migrates a backup to a new instance and attempts to navigate to an old ticket, no redirect will occur and the user might not know where the ticket was moved. It would be useful if we could find a way to retain the redirect information.

